{"title":"Manim3 UsingText","uid":"60bd8fd469f282ac6b13a9d5e27c3f6b","slug":"manim/C3 UsingText","date":"2021-08-26T03:46:33.000Z","updated":"2021-08-26T07:59:20.369Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/manim/C3 UsingText.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"使用文本\"><a href=\"#使用文本\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用文本\"></a>使用文本</h1><h2 id=\"without-LaTeX-​​\"><a href=\"#without-LaTeX-​​\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"without $LaTeX$​​\"></a>without $LaTeX$​​</h2><h3 id=\"文本\"><a href=\"#文本\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"文本\"></a>文本</h3><p><code>helloworld.py</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> manim <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">HelloWorld</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Scene<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">construct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        text <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Text<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Hello world\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>scale<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>add<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gtu8yiyjvcj60nq0dcwen02.jpg\" alt=\"HelloWorld_ManimCE_v0.9.0\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"带颜色文本\"><a href=\"#带颜色文本\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"带颜色文本\"></a>带颜色文本</h3><p><code>MarkupText.py</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> manim <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">SingleLineColor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Scene<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">construct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        text <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> MarkupText<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-interpolation\"><span class=\"token string\">f'all in red &lt;span fgcolor=\"</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>YELLOW<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span></span><span class=\"token string\">\">except this&lt;/span>'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> color<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>RED<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>add<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"不同字体\"><a href=\"#不同字体\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"不同字体\"></a>不同字体</h3><p>``</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> manim <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FontsExample</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Scene<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">construct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        ft <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Text<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Noto Sans\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> font<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Noto Sans\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>add<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>ft<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"设置倾斜和权重\"><a href=\"#设置倾斜和权重\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"设置倾斜和权重\"></a>设置倾斜和权重</h3><p>倾斜</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> manim <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">SlantsExample</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Scene<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">construct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Text<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Italic\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> slant<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>ITALIC<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>add<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>权重</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> manim <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">DifferentWeight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Scene<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">construct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> manimpango\n\n        g <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> VGroup<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        weight_list <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">dict</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token builtin\">sorted</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>weight<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> manimpango<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Weight<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>weight<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> weight <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> manimpango<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Weight<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>items<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> key<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token keyword\">lambda</span> x<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> x<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> weight <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> weight_list<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            g <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> Text<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>weight<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> weight<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>weight<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> font<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Open Sans\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>add<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>g<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>arrange<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>DOWN<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>scale<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>颜色</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> manim <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">SimpleColor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Scene<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">construct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        col <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Text<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"RED COLOR\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> color<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>RED<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>add<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>col<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>特定字符着色</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> manim <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Textt2cExample</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Scene<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">construct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        t2cindices <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Text<span clas